      "content": "### 解题思路\n1. 思路\n    - Python3中的除法是`向下取整`。示例：`3/-2=-1.5` 向下取整为`-2`，所以`3//-2=-2`\n    - 转换公式：`N,mod=-(N>>1),N%2`\n\n### 代码\n\n```python3\nclass Solution:\n    def baseNeg2(self, N: int) -> str:\n        res=\"\"\n        while N:\n            N,mod=-(N>>1),N%2\n            res=str(mod)+res\n        return res if res else \"0\"\n```",
